<item xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" n="4" xml:id="addition4">
    <locus from="200b" to="200b"/>
    <p>On fol. 200 b, at the end of <ref target="#b4">the Gospel of S. John</ref>, there is a note, unfortunately mutilated, stating that the last two leaves were written by one <persName ref="">Gabriel of Edessa</persName>: </p>
    <p>
        <quote xml:lang="syr">ܨܠܘ ܥܠ ܚܛܝܐ . . . ܓܒܪܝܠ ܒܪ ܡـ . . . ܐ ܩܝܢܝܐ ܡܢ ܐܘܪܗܝ ܡـ[ܕܝܢܬܐ ܪܚܡܬ] ܠܡܫܝܚܐ ܕܢܚܣܐ ܠܗ ܡܪܝܐ ܘ . . . ܘܝܐ ܘܠܟܬܘܒܐ ܘ܏ܫ.</quote>
    </p>
</item>
