    <locus from="205" to="205"/>
    <p>At the end of <ref target="#b4">the Gospel of S. John</ref>, after the subscription, stands the following doxology:</p>
    <p>
        <quote xml:lang="syr">
            <sic>ܫܘܒܐ  ܠܐܒܐ: ܕܥܕܪ ; ܘܠܒܪܐ: ܕܣܝ̇ܥ ܘܠܪܘܚܐ. ܩܕܝܫܐ. ܕܫ̇ܡܠ̣ܝ</sic>
